OL,6,FA 'serious fire' ripped through a
OL,7,Frestaurant in Guernsey in the early
OL,8,Fhours of Saturday 24 February.
OL,10,FThe fire produced a 'toxic smoke
OL,11,Fflume', islanders have been warned to
OL,12,Fkeep their doors and windows closed if
OL,13,Fthey see smoke coming towards them.
OL,15,FHowever, Guernsey Fire Service
OL,16,FIncident Commander, Danny Joyce has
OL,17,Fstressed: "It is not a public safety
OL,18,Fhazard."
OL,20,FEmergency services attended the blaze
OL,21,Fat Octopus restaurant,, at 4.09 am.
